Filesystem
----------

* relative resolved against existing file/dir

* file()/directory() in path/file/dir (i.e. subdir/file)

* directory files/dirs/paths

* exists() should check the type for file/dir

* directory mkdir/rmdir  create/delete

* directory children/files/directories/dirs

* file read/write/text/lines/etc

* virtual filesystems with a non-root root

* virtual filesystems composed across several real filesystems


